The paper discusses training techniques and metrics for personalization of deep learning models, which falls under the category of machine learning. The focus is on optimizing performance metrics for a particular individual while conforming to certain constraints. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
